<RECORDNO>975044635</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
THE rapturous reception given to President Clinton from all sections of the
Northern Irish community suggests a solution of the Northern Ireland problem.
Northern Ireland should become the 51st state of the United States of America!
Robert F Gibson,
2 Southview Drive,
Blanefield.
